    "- King, R.F. (1955). The remanent magnetism of artificially deposited sediments. *Mon. Not. R. Astron. Soc.* 7, 115\u2013134.\n",
    "- Cao, X. et al. (2024). *Earth System Science Data* 16, 4007\u20134032.\n",
