    "- Tian, D., Uieda, L., Leong, W.J., Fr\u00f6hlich, Y., Schlitzer, W., Grund, M., Jones, M., Toney, L., Yao, J., Magen, Y., Tong, J.-H., Ngo, L., Materna, K., Belem, A., Newton, T., Anant, A., Ziebarth, M., Quinn, J. & Wessel, P. (2024). PyGMT: A Python interface for the Generic Mapping Tools. *Zenodo*. https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10578540\n",
